<li>However , the fact that YdeO induced yhiE but GadX did not suggests that YdeO binds to the downstream region of hdeD .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12694615" target="_blank">12694615</a>]<br></li>
<li>Many of the YdeO-activated genes were also activated by GadX , whereas yhiEUV were induced only by YdeO .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=12694615" target="_blank">12694615</a>]<br></li>
